[Episode 21]

4
00:01:35,480 --> 00:01:36,630
How dare you!

5
00:01:36,630 --> 00:01:37,630
How dare you tie me up!

6
00:01:41,510 --> 00:01:42,040
Who is he?

7
00:01:43,590 --> 00:01:44,270
He is...

8
00:01:45,400 --> 00:01:47,270
This is the son of Governor Qi,

9
00:01:47,440 --> 00:01:50,120
Mr. Qi,
the Deputy Commandant of Pingyangwei.

10
00:01:51,830 --> 00:01:53,270
He's here looking for Miss Luo.

11
00:01:53,440 --> 00:01:55,360
They are both my friends.

12
00:01:55,870 --> 00:01:57,120
The servants just misunderstood.

13
00:01:57,480 --> 00:01:59,400
Right, we're all friends.

14
00:02:00,870 --> 00:02:01,720
Who are you?

15
00:02:04,440 --> 00:02:07,800
I am Zhou Xian,
the county school instructor of Linfen.

16
00:02:08,440 --> 00:02:09,670
I didn't recognize you.

17
00:02:10,000 --> 00:02:11,320
Please forgive me.

18
00:02:11,600 --> 00:02:12,520
Forgive me.

19
00:02:15,110 --> 00:02:16,160
You damn fools...

20
00:02:16,160 --> 00:02:17,830
How could you capture Mr. Qi?

21
00:02:18,520 --> 00:02:19,910
Mr. Zhou, it's a misunderstanding!

22
00:02:19,910 --> 00:02:20,470
We saw

23
00:02:20,470 --> 00:02:21,440
Mr. Qi riding on the wall,

24
00:02:21,440 --> 00:02:22,240
so we grabbed him.

25
00:02:22,320 --> 00:02:22,880
I...

26
00:02:22,880 --> 00:02:24,440
Mr. Qi was anxious to find me.

27
00:02:24,670 --> 00:02:25,800
That's why this happened.

28
00:02:26,030 --> 00:02:26,880
I knocked on your door.

29
00:02:27,030 --> 00:02:28,030
Why didn't you open it?

30
00:02:29,320 --> 00:02:30,110
Exactly!

31
00:02:30,390 --> 00:02:31,800
You servants

32
00:02:31,800 --> 00:02:33,030
can't even recognize Mr. Qi.

33
00:02:33,110 --> 00:02:34,320
Hurry up and get out of here.

34
00:02:34,600 --> 00:02:35,270
Yes!

35
00:02:39,390 --> 00:02:40,360
It's a misunderstanding.

36
00:02:41,390 --> 00:02:43,470
Commandant Qi, you're very magnanimous.

37
00:02:44,440 --> 00:02:45,750
Don't take it to heart.

38
00:02:50,800 --> 00:02:51,880
But that thing

39
00:02:52,270 --> 00:02:53,270
was really found

40
00:02:53,270 --> 00:02:55,000
in Mrs. Zhou's room.

41
00:02:55,360 --> 00:02:56,470
It doesn't belong to Commandant Qi...

42
00:02:56,470 --> 00:02:57,030
Xian,

43
00:02:57,030 --> 00:02:57,800
I truly didn't do

44
00:02:57,800 --> 00:02:58,910
to wrong you.

45
00:02:58,910 --> 00:03:00,110
You have to believe me. I...

46
00:03:00,110 --> 00:03:01,270
Enough with the noise!

47
00:03:04,800 --> 00:03:05,600
Mr. Qi.

48
00:03:06,670 --> 00:03:09,390
Sorry for my family drama.

49
00:03:10,030 --> 00:03:11,030
It's rare for you to visit.

50
00:03:11,030 --> 00:03:12,110
Let me

51
00:03:12,110 --> 00:03:13,320
prepare a feast for you

52
00:03:13,720 --> 00:03:14,670
to show my apologies.

53
00:03:15,080 --> 00:03:15,880
Xian,

54
00:03:16,160 --> 00:03:17,720
I need to talk with Miss Luo

55
00:03:17,720 --> 00:03:18,830
and Mr. Qi.

56
00:03:20,470 --> 00:03:22,320
Okay! Go ahead and chat.

57
00:03:23,270 --> 00:03:24,080
Mr. Qi.

58
00:03:24,360 --> 00:03:28,000
If you need anything, just let me know.

59
00:03:33,390 --> 00:03:34,750
Take care of your household matters.

60
00:03:35,470 --> 00:03:36,270
Yes!

61
00:03:52,360 --> 00:03:53,600
There are outsiders here.

62
00:03:54,670 --> 00:03:56,080
I can't ask too much.

63
00:04:00,190 --> 00:04:01,550
But about today's incident,

64
00:04:02,960 --> 00:04:05,080
you must give me an explanation.

65
00:04:07,110 --> 00:04:08,470
I didn't do it.

66
00:04:08,720 --> 00:04:10,470
How can I explain that to you?

67
00:04:10,600 --> 00:04:12,160
Well, this...

68
00:04:12,320 --> 00:04:13,160
Xian.

69
00:04:13,270 --> 00:04:14,440
Calm down!

70
00:04:14,880 --> 00:04:16,720
Our son will wake up from his nap soon.

71
00:04:17,160 --> 00:04:18,670
He'll definitely be clamoring for you.

72
00:04:19,000 --> 00:04:20,160
Let's head back for now.

73
00:05:08,200 --> 00:05:10,830
I was wrong earlier.

74
00:05:12,390 --> 00:05:13,950
I apologize again, Miss Luo.

75
00:05:17,200 --> 00:05:18,880
Miss Liu,
you don't need to be so formal.

76
00:05:20,640 --> 00:05:22,110
Today, my relatives

77
00:05:22,640 --> 00:05:23,830
offended Mr. Qi.

78
00:05:24,640 --> 00:05:25,830
I apologize on their behalf.

79
00:05:29,950 --> 00:05:31,200
Today, for Luo Shu's sake,

80
00:05:31,200 --> 00:05:32,440
I won't hold it against you.

81
00:05:32,830 --> 00:05:34,320
But if you bully Luo Shu again,

82
00:05:35,000 --> 00:05:35,720
I won't be

83
00:05:35,720 --> 00:05:36,760
so easy to deal with next time.

84
00:05:40,000 --> 00:05:40,670
Let's go.

85
00:05:40,670 --> 00:05:41,200
Wait!

86
00:05:42,950 --> 00:05:43,640
I've heard

87
00:05:43,640 --> 00:05:45,390
that you're skilled in investigations.

88
00:05:45,920 --> 00:05:47,790
Can I ask for your advice?

89
00:05:48,600 --> 00:05:49,230
Okay!

90
00:05:49,600 --> 00:05:51,440
Can I invite you

91
00:05:51,440 --> 00:05:52,720
to stay here for a few days?

92
00:05:53,000 --> 00:05:54,270
It'll be easier for me
to consult with you.

93
00:05:54,720 --> 00:05:55,510
Miss Liu.

94
00:05:56,040 --> 00:05:57,070
You use Luo Shu when needed,

95
00:05:57,070 --> 00:05:58,230
but ignore her when not.

96
00:05:58,920 --> 00:05:59,950
For investigating,

97
00:06:00,640 --> 00:06:01,790
shouldn't you be asking Han Muzhi?

98
00:06:06,070 --> 00:06:07,600
It's obvious

99
00:06:07,640 --> 00:06:09,600
that Wenyin is being framed.

100
00:06:10,200 --> 00:06:11,720
But I don't know how to help her.

101
00:06:12,480 --> 00:06:13,950
She's a refined lady

102
00:06:14,320 --> 00:06:15,320
with a reserved temperament.

103
00:06:15,510 --> 00:06:17,790
If this isn't cleared up,

104
00:06:18,230 --> 00:06:19,230
her future will...

105
00:06:19,230 --> 00:06:20,760
Honestly, I can see it.

106
00:06:21,760 --> 00:06:22,640
She doesn't seem like the type

107
00:06:22,640 --> 00:06:24,040
to do something like that.

108
00:06:24,390 --> 00:06:25,830
You're really good at investigations.

109
00:06:27,160 --> 00:06:28,160
Please help me.

110
00:06:30,230 --> 00:06:31,270
It depends on who.

111
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:33,070
You're so capable.

112
00:06:33,390 --> 00:06:34,320
You can handle it yourself.

113
00:06:36,110 --> 00:06:38,000
I will help you
get to the bottom of this case.

114
00:06:38,110 --> 00:06:39,510
It's my responsibility.

115
00:06:39,830 --> 00:06:40,640
What are you doing?

116
00:06:41,320 --> 00:06:42,670
This isn't your concern.

117
00:06:42,790 --> 00:06:44,350
It shouldn't be my problem.

118
00:06:44,640 --> 00:06:46,320
But you jumped over the wall to find me,

119
00:06:46,600 --> 00:06:48,320
and caused such a big misunderstanding.

120
00:06:48,390 --> 00:06:49,510
So now it involves me.

121
00:06:49,670 --> 00:06:50,320
I...

122
00:06:53,720 --> 00:06:54,350
Fine.

123
00:06:56,160 --> 00:06:57,160
Since you stay,

124
00:06:58,200 --> 00:06:59,600
I won't leave either.

125
00:07:03,480 --> 00:07:04,790
Are you worried your reputation

126
00:07:04,790 --> 00:07:06,000
isn't ruined enough?

127
00:07:07,200 --> 00:07:08,000
What if

128
00:07:08,000 --> 00:07:08,790
you're alone here

129
00:07:10,230 --> 00:07:11,070
and someone

130
00:07:11,070 --> 00:07:11,790
bullies you again?

131
00:07:13,950 --> 00:07:15,070
Don't worry, Mr. Qi.

132
00:07:16,270 --> 00:07:17,880
I need Miss Luo's help.

133
00:07:18,830 --> 00:07:20,200
I make sure she will be treated well.

134
00:07:23,040 --> 00:07:24,110
Can you do me a favor?

135
00:07:24,110 --> 00:07:24,950
What do you need?

136
00:07:24,950 --> 00:07:26,390
Help me take a leave from the yamen.

137
00:07:26,790 --> 00:07:27,920
Just say I'm at a friend's place

138
00:07:27,920 --> 00:07:28,920
for a few days.

139
00:07:28,920 --> 00:07:30,110
I won't be back for now.

140
00:07:30,320 --> 00:07:31,720
You also want me to help you take leave?

141
00:07:32,000 --> 00:07:32,830
Well, I owe you

142
00:07:32,830 --> 00:07:33,880
a lot of favors.

143
00:07:33,920 --> 00:07:34,950
This counts as one.

144
00:07:37,320 --> 00:07:38,440
The more you owe me, the better.

145
00:07:39,110 --> 00:07:39,920
Besides,

146
00:07:40,320 --> 00:07:41,320
staying away from Han Muzhi
for a few days

147
00:07:41,320 --> 00:07:41,950
is good.

148
00:07:42,920 --> 00:07:43,720
What do you say?

149
00:07:45,830 --> 00:07:46,480
Then...

150
00:07:48,160 --> 00:07:49,040
Since that's the case,

151
00:07:49,040 --> 00:07:50,040
I'll

152
00:07:50,040 --> 00:07:51,070
help you out.

153
00:07:51,640 --> 00:07:52,440
And...

154
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:54,320
Don't mention Miss Liu,

155
00:07:54,440 --> 00:07:55,670
especially not to Magistrate Han.

156
00:07:59,950 --> 00:08:00,920
I warn you,

157
00:08:01,600 --> 00:08:03,000
you must treat Luo Shu well.

158
00:08:03,600 --> 00:08:04,880
If she gets hurt again,

159
00:08:05,550 --> 00:08:06,510
I won't let you off easily.

160
00:08:11,550 --> 00:08:13,070
Yue is so aggressive.

161
00:08:13,790 --> 00:08:15,110
I have no evidence,

162
00:08:15,510 --> 00:08:17,000
so I can only let her slander me.

163
00:08:17,720 --> 00:08:18,720
I can never

164
00:08:18,720 --> 00:08:19,950
clear my name.

165
00:08:20,550 --> 00:08:22,070
Though Yue is a concubine,

166
00:08:22,480 --> 00:08:24,230
she acts without restraint.

167
00:08:24,670 --> 00:08:26,200
What's the reason for this?

168
00:08:29,950 --> 00:08:31,600
It's my fault.

169
00:08:33,080 --> 00:08:34,760
After marrying into the Zhou family
for so many years,

170
00:08:35,760 --> 00:08:37,910
I haven't had a child.

171
00:08:38,590 --> 00:08:39,760
But Yue

172
00:08:40,200 --> 00:08:41,280
bore the only son

173
00:08:41,280 --> 00:08:42,550
for the Zhou family.

174
00:08:43,550 --> 00:08:45,000
Of course, she's bold.

175
00:08:45,200 --> 00:08:46,550
But you're his wife.

176
00:08:48,640 --> 00:08:51,760
She grew up with Xian.

177
00:08:52,760 --> 00:08:54,150
I'm the outsider here.

178
00:08:54,670 --> 00:08:56,200
How could I compete

179
00:08:56,230 --> 00:08:58,080
with their childhood bond?

180
00:08:58,910 --> 00:09:00,280
Did you know about this earlier?

181
00:09:04,000 --> 00:09:05,470
After two years of marriage
into the Zhou family,

182
00:09:06,030 --> 00:09:07,320
I still have no children.

183
00:09:08,400 --> 00:09:10,230
So Zhou Xian suggested
taking a concubine.

184
00:09:11,200 --> 00:09:13,350
Though I was unwilling,

185
00:09:14,550 --> 00:09:15,960
for the sake of the Zhou family,

186
00:09:17,230 --> 00:09:18,350
for Xian,

187
00:09:18,400 --> 00:09:19,840
I had to compromise.

188
00:09:21,550 --> 00:09:23,030
After Xian took her in,

189
00:09:24,710 --> 00:09:25,790
I found out

190
00:09:28,280 --> 00:09:30,760
she and Xian had been betrothed before.

191
00:09:31,590 --> 00:09:32,520
After breaking off the engagement,

192
00:09:33,320 --> 00:09:35,280
Xian came to my family to propose.

193
00:09:37,030 --> 00:09:38,350
Once she moved in,

194
00:09:40,080 --> 00:09:42,000
Xian showered her with affection,

195
00:09:42,200 --> 00:09:43,790
while he was cold to me.

196
00:09:44,640 --> 00:09:46,230
Last year, my father passed away,

197
00:09:46,400 --> 00:09:48,030
and she had a son.

198
00:09:48,960 --> 00:09:50,670
So my life in the Zhou family...

199
00:09:55,110 --> 00:09:56,550
I know he married me

200
00:09:57,710 --> 00:09:59,640
because my father was an official,

201
00:10:00,400 --> 00:10:01,910
which is beneficial for his career.

202
00:10:03,230 --> 00:10:05,150
But now, things have changed.

203
00:10:06,440 --> 00:10:07,910
All I can do

204
00:10:07,910 --> 00:10:09,590
is live

205
00:10:09,790 --> 00:10:11,440
by his moods.

206
00:10:11,590 --> 00:10:12,960
If you keep putting up with her,

207
00:10:13,470 --> 00:10:14,670
you'll just encourage her

208
00:10:15,110 --> 00:10:16,910
to think you're weak
and easy to bully.

209
00:10:26,590 --> 00:10:27,670
I used to think

210
00:10:28,590 --> 00:10:29,640
I could just put up with it,

211
00:10:30,110 --> 00:10:31,640
keep my distance,

212
00:10:31,640 --> 00:10:32,710
and let it go.

213
00:10:33,520 --> 00:10:34,550
But now,

214
00:10:35,790 --> 00:10:37,710
she's actually trying to

215
00:10:37,710 --> 00:10:39,280
do anything to get the wife position.

216
00:10:40,200 --> 00:10:42,440
She even wants Zhou Xian to divorce me.

217
00:10:43,910 --> 00:10:45,710
If I keep putting up with this,

218
00:10:46,280 --> 00:10:48,440
I might end up not only being thrown out

219
00:10:50,150 --> 00:10:52,440
but also living in shame.

220
00:10:54,960 --> 00:10:55,760
Miss Luo,

221
00:10:56,640 --> 00:10:58,470
Wenyin has already
suffered too much.

222
00:10:59,230 --> 00:11:01,760
So I'm counting on you for this.

223
00:11:06,440 --> 00:11:08,230
To prove your innocence,

224
00:11:09,280 --> 00:11:11,470
we first need to find out
who the man is.

225
00:11:17,200 --> 00:11:20,000
At that time, Madam was taking a nap,

226
00:11:20,520 --> 00:11:21,280
and I came back from outside

227
00:11:21,280 --> 00:11:23,200
with some embroidery patterns.

228
00:11:27,000 --> 00:11:28,670
Did you see what the person looked like?

229
00:11:30,000 --> 00:11:30,910
I was too far away

230
00:11:30,910 --> 00:11:32,470
to see his face clearly.

231
00:11:32,760 --> 00:11:35,320
But I felt he was tall

232
00:11:35,520 --> 00:11:36,910
and very agile.

233
00:11:39,000 --> 00:11:40,640
This person could sneak into your room

234
00:11:40,640 --> 00:11:41,590
to leave the underwear,

235
00:11:42,080 --> 00:11:43,280
so he must have planned it beforehand.

236
00:11:44,080 --> 00:11:46,000
He even chose the time
when you were napping.

237
00:11:46,320 --> 00:11:47,670
It shows he knows

238
00:11:47,670 --> 00:11:48,790
the inner courtyard well.

239
00:11:53,150 --> 00:11:54,470
Who usually has access

240
00:11:54,470 --> 00:11:55,640
to the inner courtyard?

241
00:11:56,030 --> 00:11:57,350
We've sent people to look around,

242
00:11:57,350 --> 00:11:58,880
but we can't find Luo Shu anywhere.

243
00:11:59,320 --> 00:12:01,200
Where could Luo Shu have gone?

244
00:12:02,030 --> 00:12:03,280
Send out more people to look for her.

245
00:12:03,760 --> 00:12:04,710
Don't come back until you find her.

246
00:12:05,200 --> 00:12:05,840
Yes.

247
00:12:05,840 --> 00:12:06,470
Stop looking for her.

248
00:12:08,200 --> 00:12:08,960
Mr. Qi.

249
00:12:08,960 --> 00:12:09,640
Magistrate Han.

250
00:12:10,440 --> 00:12:11,550
I'm here to take leave for Luo Shu.

251
00:12:12,640 --> 00:12:13,400
Where is she?

252
00:12:13,440 --> 00:12:14,200
She's at a friend's place.

253
00:12:14,200 --> 00:12:15,320
She said she'll be away for a few days.

254
00:12:15,440 --> 00:12:16,230
What friend?

255
00:12:17,230 --> 00:12:18,110
Maybe someone she knew before.

256
00:12:18,110 --> 00:12:18,960
I'm not sure.

257
00:12:19,550 --> 00:12:21,470
Anyway, I brought the message.

258
00:12:22,520 --> 00:12:24,320
I have other things to do,
so I'll go now.

259
00:12:27,880 --> 00:12:28,590
What were you doing

260
00:12:28,590 --> 00:12:29,440
at noon?

261
00:12:29,440 --> 00:12:30,280
I was planting flowers.

262
00:12:30,470 --> 00:12:31,550
After planting,

263
00:12:31,760 --> 00:12:32,910
I went to eat.

264
00:12:32,910 --> 00:12:33,640
We had lunch at home

265
00:12:33,640 --> 00:12:35,110
and then

266
00:12:35,150 --> 00:12:36,350
came to work.

267
00:12:36,350 --> 00:12:36,790
Same here.

268
00:12:36,790 --> 00:12:38,110
I was with my master.

269
00:12:38,110 --> 00:12:39,710
I was fixing the roof
of the west courtyard.

270
00:12:39,710 --> 00:12:40,790
The roof was leaking,

271
00:12:40,790 --> 00:12:42,280
so I added a few tiles.

272
00:12:42,590 --> 00:12:43,590
This isn't that person either.

273
00:12:54,280 --> 00:12:55,080
How about it?

274
00:12:55,320 --> 00:12:56,640
Have you found anything?

275
00:13:03,440 --> 00:13:04,320
If this man

276
00:13:04,320 --> 00:13:05,960
was indeed sent by Yue,

277
00:13:06,760 --> 00:13:08,550
even if he hasn't entered
the inner courtyard,

278
00:13:09,320 --> 00:13:10,400
Yue would tell him

279
00:13:10,400 --> 00:13:11,590
about the situation inside.

280
00:13:11,960 --> 00:13:13,590
But that makes it too broad.

281
00:13:13,640 --> 00:13:15,080
There's no way to trace it.

282
00:13:17,030 --> 00:13:17,840
Do you know

283
00:13:17,840 --> 00:13:19,590
any men who are close with Yue?

284
00:13:23,760 --> 00:13:25,320
I heard from the cook

285
00:13:25,470 --> 00:13:26,320
that Yue

286
00:13:26,320 --> 00:13:27,670
arranged for a distant cousin

287
00:13:27,670 --> 00:13:29,230
to be a groom in the house.

288
00:13:29,840 --> 00:13:30,910
What's this person like?

289
